feel as if they were physically present in a pool hall.\n\nSome of the planned features include:\n\n- Single Player unlockables, achievements, and Puzzle mode!\n- Online Cooperation Mode.\n- More AI opponents\n- Additional avatars, locations, and utilities.\n- Physics, sounds, and UI improvements.\n- Spectator mode\n\nAnd much more!\n\nStay tuned, and join the 8 Ball Club!", "short_description": "Welcome to the December 2024 Community Update!\n\n- 110,000 Active Users <3 Thank you for Support!\n- Free Trial Play is here, along with new difficulty levels and an Auto Matchmaking System that quickly pairs you with a tailored AI opponent if line takes too long.\n\nPlay now the most realistic VR 8 ball pool game! Engage in thrilling matches against AI opponents or connect with friends around the world for a real-time pool face-off."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sharpforks.com/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://sharpforks.com/term-of-use/", "publisher_name": "Sharp Forks Labs", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sharpforks.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED", "genres": ["SPORTS", "SOCIAL"], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "9463050907056927"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-fra5-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031334_859614622916331_20